summary:
Have lovely Christmas days and a beautiful new year. 2019 is going to be awesome! Enjoy it.

Dear one, we have connected with...
caption:
Have lovely Christmas days and a beautiful new year. 2019 is going to be awesome! Enjoy it.

Dear one, we have connected with you in so many ways this year and we love to do that in the next year too. We have been sharing our love, experience, knowledge with you about yoga and related activities to help you balance body ~ mind ~ spirit to gain and keep health and happiness.

You are very dear to us! We may not tell you this often, but our wishes for you are always to bring you safety, peace, harmony, balance, health and happiness.
Shine bright in your own uniqueness, standing in the light of your true self.
We love to see you shine!

Love & Light,
saktiisha team
